Apa? "Sial"?

335
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:32,020
Astaga.

336
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:33,699
Maafkan aku.
Seharusnya aku berhati-hati.

337
00:22:33,699 --> 00:22:35,500
Astaga, jangan bilang begitu.

